# 1. Product Page Videos and Conversion Rates\
\
## Study: Skeepers Ecommerce Video Case Study\
\
Results from adding consumer demonstration videos directly to product pages.\
\
Metrics:\
\
* **+21.5% increase in conversion rate**\
* **+50% increase in add-to-cart rate**\
\
Source\
[https://skeepers.io/case-studies/la-redoute/](https://skeepers.io/case-studies/la-redoute/)\
\
Notes\
\
The videos used in this test were **consumer demonstration videos**, which closely resemble influencer product review content.\
