\
# 7. Interpretation of Data (Evidence-Based)\
\
The research consistently shows two patterns:\
\
### Product Trust\
\
Product videos and creator demonstrations increase understanding of the product and reduce uncertainty, leading to higher conversion rates.\
\
### Purchase Friction\
\
Sticky add-to-cart buttons improve conversion by keeping the purchase action visible during the browsing process.\
\
