\
The data suggests combining:\
\
1. **Influencer / creator product video**\
2. **Sticky mobile add-to-cart**\
\
Because they target different parts of the decision process.\
\
Trust driver\
\
* product video\
\
Friction reducer\
\
* persistent purchase CTA\
